<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: hsl(240, 10%, 4%);
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .error-box { max-width: 480px; padding: 2rem; }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(200,95%,45%), hsl(170,70%,50%));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .error-icon { font-size: 3rem; margin: 1rem 0; opacity: 0.6; }
        h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        p { color: #888; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
        a {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(200,95%,45%), hsl(170,70%,50%));
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        a:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-box">
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <div class="error-icon"><i class="fas fa-compass"></i></div>
        <h2>Page Not Found</h2>
        <p>The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved.</p>
        <a href="/"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
